Package: hammr
Type: Package
Title: Hammr - general utility functions
Version: 1.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Stefan", "Fleck", email = "stefan.fleck@statistik.gv.at", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Stefan Fleck <stefan.fleck@statistik.gv.at>
Description: This package contains various utility functions and 
  shortcuts that I use throughout my other packages. Some are useful in a 
  general way (such as the df_* functions), other were designed for very 
  specific tasks (such as vec_match_seq and date_yq). Use at your own risk.
